  "detailed_description": "<i> Dead? Alive? Both? </i><br>Help Einstein the cat restore reality before his owners come home to a dangerously unstable alternate dimension.<br><br>In this fast paced retro platform game, you must think fast as you run, jump and swap colour, making your way through 8 floors of challenging and amusing colour changing mayhem. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771200/extras/aa6b1d8dd5ec83625de53c5df00e3d0f.poster.avif?t=1694891936\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771200/extras/aa6b1d8dd5ec83625de53c5df00e3d0f.webm?t=1694891936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771200/extras/aa6b1d8dd5ec83625de53c5df00e3d0f.mp4?t=1694891936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>    Unique colour changing gameplay<br></li><li>    Fast, fun and challenging experience<br></li><li>    Local 2 player co-op mode (Joypad required for player 2)<br></li><li>    Assist mode<br></li><li>    8-Bit retro inspired graphics & sound<br></li><li>    8 floors of varied level design (spread over 64 uniquely themed levels)<br></li><li>    Secret challenge levels to unlock<br></li><li>    Hats for cats!<br></li><li>    Cat puns galore!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<i> Dead? Alive? Both? </i><br>Help Einstein the cat restore reality before his owners come home to a dangerously unstable alternate dimension.<br><br>In this fast paced retro platform game, you must think fast as you run, jump and swap colour, making your way through 8 floors of challenging and amusing colour changing mayhem. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771200/extras/aa6b1d8dd5ec83625de53c5df00e3d0f.poster.avif?t=1694891936\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771200/extras/aa6b1d8dd5ec83625de53c5df00e3d0f.webm?t=1694891936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771200/extras/aa6b1d8dd5ec83625de53c5df00e3d0f.mp4?t=1694891936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>    Unique colour changing gameplay<br></li><li>    Fast, fun and challenging experience<br></li><li>    Local 2 player co-op mode (Joypad required for player 2)<br></li><li>    Assist mode<br></li><li>    8-Bit retro inspired graphics & sound<br></li><li>    8 floors of varied level design (spread over 64 uniquely themed levels)<br></li><li>    Secret challenge levels to unlock<br></li><li>    Hats for cats!<br></li><li>    Cat puns galore!</li></ul>",
